nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|A Kib questioned whether North could pass since the hand is balanced, would pass have been better? Balanced means the hand has no singletons or voids. It is true that balanced hands are not nearly as strong as unbalanced hands with equivalent high card points.|
